    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/63e1de4c46f85a39a825b1fdfda55e62.webp?t=1757699243\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/60d04231a6b064bc3bb278a0c7e50983.poster.avif?t=1757699243\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/60d04231a6b064bc3bb278a0c7e50983.webm?t=1757699243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/60d04231a6b064bc3bb278a0c7e50983.mp4?t=1757699243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提升军衔，成为传奇指挥官。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控潜艇武器，带领它迎战强大的敌方船队！使用鱼雷击沉敌方舰队，晋升为潜艇舰队的海军上将。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/acbd6cd9fae162a8ded9e164ade3aabc.webp?t=1757699243\" width=600 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/56d3a48acd8ede207d54fa5e4aeabcf6.poster.avif?t=1757699243\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/56d3a48acd8ede207d54fa5e4aeabcf6.webm?t=1757699243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164760/extras/56d3a48acd8ede207d54fa5e4aeabcf6.mp4?t=1757699243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>投身于与敌方舰队的战术海战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索北极荒原、峡谷、深渊和沉没神庙的水下区域，获取战术优势并准备伏击。参加海上活动、战术任务和海军挑战，获取珍贵资源。统治海洋，展现你的海军实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多样的真实舰船：精准追踪并摧毁真实的军舰。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实的损伤效果：体验多种类型的激烈战斗场景。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三种游戏模式：参与海战、解放领土或完成尽可能多的任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级与弹药：提升潜艇属性，装备多种导弹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >增益道具：利用护甲、空中支援、瞬时装填、热成像等道具获得优势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >额外任务：发现并摧毁所有敌方飞机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >震撼的画面与场景：沉浸于逼真的视觉效果中。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好迎接终极海战模拟器了吗？</p>",
